                "content": "<p>很开心知乎下面没有看到微博上的谣言</p><p>根据美国农业部最新数据，埃塞俄比亚大豆产量将增长5k公吨在MY18/19达到12万公吨。此前在2017.6-2018.2期间，印度越南分别进口埃塞俄比亚26576MT及20284MT大豆，占比达到埃塞大豆产量79％，同期中国进口量为5148MT，仅占9％。最近一期埃塞进口8900MT vs 出口48000MT</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a4f22e3546a67e3294c077470720b7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1263\" data-rawheight=\"651\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2e73e1a373d335f0be44bd968a9cf58a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1263\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-65a4f22e3546a67e3294c077470720b7_r.jpg\"></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1263'%20height='651'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1263\" data-rawheight=\"651\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2e73e1a373d335f0be44bd968a9cf58a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1263\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-65a4f22e3546a67e3294c077470720b7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a4f22e3546a67e3294c077470720b7_b.jpg\"></figure><p><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c7ef033f42e6492aae41148f2987df5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"957\" data-rawheight=\"104\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"957\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9c7ef033f42e6492aae41148f2987df5_r.jpg\"></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='957'%20height='104'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"957\" data-rawheight=\"104\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"957\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9c7ef033f42e6492aae41148f2987df5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9c7ef033f42e6492aae41148f2987df5_b.jpg\"></figure><p><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\